"No profile" = "未添加";
"Detection mode never starts Fantastic Island's managed Mihomo workflow. Use it when you already have another Clash client running and only want Fantastic Island to inspect or control that client." = "探测模式不会启动 Fantastic Island 内建的 Mihomo。适合你已经有其他 Clash 客户端在运行，只希望 Fantastic Island 读取或控制那个客户端的时候使用。";
"Managed mode uses Fantastic Island's profile library and managed Mihomo workflow. Use it when you want Fantastic Island to manage subscriptions and runtime behavior itself." = "托管模式会使用 Fantastic Island 自己的配置库和内建 Mihomo。适合你希望把订阅和运行时行为都交给 Fantastic Island 管理的时候使用。";
"Detection Settings" = "探测配置";
"Point Fantastic Island at the Clash API and optional config file from the client you already use. Fantastic Island only reads and controls that existing runtime." = "把 Fantastic Island 指向你当前正在使用的 Clash API，以及可选的配置文件路径。Fantastic Island 只会读取和控制那个现有运行时。";
"Managed Profiles" = "托管配置";
"Add, rename, delete, and switch the YAML profiles that Fantastic Island can run in managed mode." = "在这里添加、重命名、删除并切换 Fantastic Island 托管模式可用的 YAML 配置。";
"Resolved Config File" = "当前配置文件";
"Leave Config File empty if you want Fantastic Island to try to discover a local Mihomo or Clash YAML file automatically." = "如果你不填写配置文件路径，Fantastic Island 会尝试自动发现本机的 Mihomo 或 Clash YAML 配置。";
"Detection Tools" = "探测工具";
"Refresh the detection result or open the API config file that Fantastic Island is currently using." = "刷新探测结果，或直接打开 Fantastic Island 当前使用的 API 配置文件。";
"Managed Tools" = "托管工具";
"Open Fantastic Island's advanced panel, inspect the generated runtime config, or jump to the managed runtime folder." = "打开 Fantastic Island 的高级面板，检查生成后的运行时配置，或直接进入托管运行时目录。";
"Recent Mihomo runtime output captured while Fantastic Island is managing the built-in runtime." = "这里显示 Fantastic Island 托管内建运行时时捕获到的最近 Mihomo 输出。";
"Switch between detection mode and managed mode, then focus on the settings and actions relevant to the mode you picked." = "在探测模式和托管模式之间切换，然后只关注你当前模式真正相关的设置和操作。";
"Network Ports" = "网络端口";
"Fantastic Island only reads the current HTTP, Socks5, and mixed proxy ports from the Clash client you already use." = "Fantastic Island 只会读取你当前 Clash 客户端里的 HTTP、Socks5 和混合代理端口。";
"Managed mode keeps the proxy ports inside Fantastic Island's runtime config so you can align Mihomo with the rest of your network setup." = "托管模式会把代理端口保存在 Fantastic Island 自己的运行时配置里，方便你统一管理 Mihomo 的网络入口。";
"Advanced Capabilities" = "高级能力";
"Inspect logs, rules, and connection overview from the detected client without leaving Fantastic Island." = "直接在 Fantastic Island 里查看探测到的 Clash 客户端日志、规则和连接概览。";
"Inspect runtime logs, current rules, and connection overview for Fantastic Island's managed Mihomo client." = "直接在 Fantastic Island 里查看托管 Mihomo 的运行日志、当前规则和连接概览。";
"Logs" = "日志";
"Rules" = "规则";
"Connections" = "连接";
"HTTP Proxy Port" = "HTTP 代理端口";
"Socks5 Proxy Port" = "Socks5 代理端口";
"Mixed Proxy Port" = "混合代理端口";
"Detection mode does not rewrite ports. Change them in the Clash client you already run, then let Fantastic Island read the updated values." = "探测模式不会改写端口。请在你正在使用的 Clash 客户端里修改端口，然后让 Fantastic Island 读取更新后的值。";
"Ports must be empty or use a value between 1 and 65535." = "端口可以留空，或者填写 1 到 65535 之间的数字。";
"Leave a field empty if you want Fantastic Island to fall back to the generated runtime defaults for that port." = "如果你希望某个端口退回到运行时配置的默认值，可以把对应输入框留空。";
"Apply Ports" = "应用端口";
"Reset" = "重置";
"Stream Mihomo logs directly inside Fantastic Island. Filtering stays local to this sheet." = "直接在 Fantastic Island 里查看 Mihomo 日志流，筛选只作用于当前弹窗。";
